title: LFG looking for group page 1 - 159
description:
This is all the lfg comics from start to 21 of june 2008.

LFG or "Looking for group" is a comic based on World of Warcraft but at the same time very different from that universe. The stpry unfolds around Richard, a homicidal Undead Warlock, and Cale anon an elve of some kind that wants to better the world.
The humor is pretty dark at times but the comic is pretty damn addictive.

This is my first torrent so any feedback about errors or problems about the torrent would be appreciated.
